snippet.title: Unables - Official Console Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Unables is a comedy physics-based puzzle game developed by 9UNZ S.A. Players will enter a world of extreme laziness to the point where characters in the game are no longer able to move. Interact and manipulate the environment around said characters. The game comes equipped with a 360-degree, slow-motion precision controls to sway, spin, push, shove, and catapult everything and everyone on screen. Play through 15 unique maps, each one with a unique setting and a backstory. Unables is launching on March 14 for PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X, and Nintendo Switch.
